room_title: Escape room "Starship Libra" by 101 Escape Rooms in Ventura
room_description: So much for your leisurely trip to Mars. You’re 3 months into your flight when you hit an asteroid storm and take catastrophic damage to the ship. Your group is the only one left on board. Your vacation plans have been scrapped-the crew has taken an escape pod home. Your job now is to save YOURSELVES! You must power up what’s left of the ship to make it to the last remaining escape pod and begin your journey home. Remaining life support systems will cease all functions in 60 minutes.
